latestIgtvVideos.title: STREET STYLE 3 Easy Ways! Ft. Metronaut by @flipkart
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Look 1 : Blue Jeans-Blue Longline Tee shirt. Half wear the wind breaker jacket.
Accessorise with chains & chunky glasses & trainer shoes with a pop of colour.

Look 2 : Select a solid shirt, keep it half open & roll a scarf around the neck, tuck it in the shirt. Round glasses & sneakers complete the look.

Look 3 : Poppy colour solid tee shirt. Slide the buckle of the belt on one side and let the open end be hanging.
A cropped jacket, picked up from women's section. A pair of sunglasses upgraded with a chain to give it an extraaaaaaa fac.
